Eyowo: Wall of Love

We’re not ones to brag, but as it turns out, people love eyowo

Providing an easier way for people to send and receive money with just their phone number has been a great honour. Here are some of the glowing things people have said about eyowo.

What is eyowo?

Eyowo is a digital solution that helps you achieve simple day-to-day financial transactions. With eyowo, you can transfer and receive money using just your phone number.

You can also fund bank accounts, pay bills and request payments. Make cardless withdrawals from ATMs anywhere in Nigeria.

Got a question?

Experience eyowo

Dial *4255# Dial *4255*100# on your mobile device and follow the prompts.
